title: Měšťané
content:
Měšťané refers to the inhabitants of the Kupecká čtvrť. More affluent than their counterparts in the Chrámová čtvrť, they have the opportunity to enjoy some of the finer things in life. But for some, not having to work means not having much of anything to do.

Zápisy do Deníku

This entry is received after retrieving Marigoldova loutna, after spending some "time" with Rozalind Pankiera. She's heard that the touch of a witcher "tingles" ...

	Nezadané měšťanky jsou většinou pod ostřížím dohledem rodičů a drženy doma. Proto jsou tak zvědavé, ale také znuděné.
